key_type_s Struct Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Encapsulates metadata about the type of an index key.

Contains the following type metadata:

  • indication of integer/float/uninterpreted
  • length (size as well as indication of fixed or variable)
  • indication of compressed or not
